@startuml TPS.Nexus 工廠看板系統 — 作業時序圖
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #0d1b2a
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #4fc3f7
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #1a3a5c
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #2a5a8c
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontColor #e0f0ff
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #0d2137
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #2a5a8c
skinparam sequenceGroupFontColor #4fc3f7
skinparam sequenceNoteBackgroundColor #1a2a3a
skinparam sequenceNoteBorderColor #2a5a8c
skinparam sequenceNoteFontColor #aac8e0
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #2a5a8c
skinparam sequenceArrowFontColor #88b8d8

title TPS.Nexus 工廠看板系統 — 作業時序圖\n(v1.3 · 2026-06-07)

actor       "使用者"              as User
participant "Browser\n(Blazor)"   as Browser
participant "KanbanMapPage"        as Page
participant "FactoryMapCanvas"     as Canvas
participant "MapEditorToolbar"     as Toolbar
participant "LayoutVersionPanel"   as VerPanel
participant "UserPrefsService"     as Prefs
participant "ILayoutService"       as LayoutSvc
participant "IEquipmentService"    as EquipSvc
participant "IAlarmService"        as AlarmSvc
participant "IMapImportService"    as MapSvc
participant "NavigationManager"    as Nav
participant "KanbanAlarmHub\n(SignalR)" as Hub
participant "DialogService"        as Dialog

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 1. 頁面初始化 ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

User    ->  Browser  : 導覽至 /kanban/{mapId}
Browser ->  Page     : OnInitializedAsync()
Page    ->  Page     : PermSvc.HasPermissionAsync\n(KANBAN_VIEW)

Page    ->  Prefs    : EnsureLoadedAsync(JS)
note right of Prefs  : 從 localStorage 讀取\nSelectedMapId

alt SelectedMapId ≠ 路由 mapId
  Page  ->  Nav      : NavigateTo(/kanban/{selectedId},\nreplace:true)
  Nav   --> Browser  : 重新導覽（early return）
end

Page    ->  MapSvc   : GetAllAsync()
MapSvc  --> Page     : AllMaps
Page    ->  LayoutSvc: GetPublishedVersionAsync(MapId)
LayoutSvc --> Page   : PublishedVersion
Page    ->  AlarmSvc : GetActiveAlarmsAsync()
AlarmSvc --> Page    : ActiveAlarms

Page    ->  Prefs    : SetSelectedMapId(MapId)\n+ SaveAsync(JS)
Page    ->  Page     : StartCarousel()
note right            : 建立 CancellationTokenSource\n篩選 CarouselEnabled 地圖\n啟動 CarouselTickAsync

Page    ->  Hub      : HubConnectionBuilder\n.WithUrl(alarmHubPath)\n.Build().StartAsync()
Hub     --> Page     : 連線成功

Page    --> Browser  : 初始 render

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 2. 地圖輪播 ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

loop 每秒 tick（PeriodicTimer）
  Page  ->  Page     : _carouselRemainingSeconds--
  Page  ->  Browser  : InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged)
  note right          : 輪播徽章倒數更新\n（position:absolute 在 wrapper 內\n全螢幕模式仍可見）
end

Page    ->  Nav      : NavigateTo("/kanban/{nextMapId}")
note right of Nav     : 同一 component 複用\n不觸發 OnInitializedAsync

Nav     ->  Page     : OnParametersSetAsync()
Page    ->  Page     : 重置狀態：\nIsEditMode = false\nShowVersions = false\n_carouselPaused = false
Page    ->  MapSvc   : GetAllAsync()
MapSvc  --> Page     : AllMaps
Page    ->  LayoutSvc: GetPublishedVersionAsync(MapId)
LayoutSvc --> Page   : PublishedVersion (new map)
Page    ->  AlarmSvc : GetActiveAlarmsAsync()
AlarmSvc --> Page    : ActiveAlarms
Page    ->  Prefs    : SetSelectedMapId(MapId) + SaveAsync(JS)
Page    ->  Page     : StartCarousel()

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 3. 編輯模式與版本發布 ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

User    ->  Toolbar  : 點擊「✏️ 編輯」
Toolbar ->  Page     : IsEditModeChanged(true)

Page    ->  LayoutSvc: GetVersionHistoryAsync(MapId)
LayoutSvc --> Page   : versions

alt 存在未發布草稿
  Page  ->  Dialog   : Confirm("是否繼續草稿？")
  Dialog --> User    : 彈出確認對話框
  User  ->  Dialog   : 繼續編輯 / 重新開始 / 取消
  alt 取消
    Dialog --> Page  : resume = null
    Page   ->  Page  : IsEditMode = false（取消進入編輯）
  else 繼續或重新開始
    Dialog --> Page  : resume = true / false
    Page   ->  Page  : _resumeDraftId = latestDraft.Id (或 null)
  end
end

Page    ->  Page     : IsEditMode = true\nStopCarousel()
Page    ->  Canvas   : re-render（編輯模式）
Canvas  ->  Browser  : JS: kanbanDrag.init\n("map-canvas", dotNetRef)
note right            : SortableJS 啟用\nwidget 可拖曳（dashed border）

User    ->  Canvas   : 拖拉設備至新位置
Canvas  ->  Browser  : JS Interop callback\nOnEquipmentMoved(equipmentId, x, y)
Browser ->  Canvas   : [JSInvokable]\nOnEquipmentMoved()
Canvas  ->  EquipSvc : SaveWidgetAsync(widget)
EquipSvc --> Canvas  : widget (updated)
Canvas  ->  Browser  : StateHasChanged

User    ->  Toolbar  : 點擊「💾 存草稿」
Toolbar ->  Page     : OnSaveDraft
Page    ->  LayoutSvc: SaveDraftAsync(MapId,\nlayoutJson, user)
LayoutSvc --> Page   : DraftId
Page    ->  Browser  : NotifySvc.Notify\n("草稿已儲存", vN)

User    ->  Toolbar  : 點擊「🚀 發布」
Toolbar ->  Page     : OnPublish
Page    ->  LayoutSvc: PublishAsync(DraftId)
LayoutSvc -> LayoutSvc: Archive 舊 Published\nDraft → Published\nPublishedAt = UtcNow
LayoutSvc --> Page   : PublishedVersion (new)
Page    ->  Page     : IsEditMode = false\n_resumeDraftId = null\n_carouselPaused = false\nStartCarousel()
Page    ->  Browser  : re-render + 成功通知

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 4. 版本面板（疊加覆蓋） ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

User    ->  Toolbar  : 點擊「📋 版本」
Toolbar ->  Page     : OnShowVersions
Page    ->  Page     : ShowVersions = true\nStopCarousel()\n_carouselPaused = true
note right            : 版本面板以 position:absolute\nz-index:300 疊加於地圖\n寬 320px，不縮小地圖區域

Page    ->  VerPanel : render
VerPanel -> LayoutSvc: GetVersionHistoryAsync(MapId)
LayoutSvc --> VerPanel: versions（降冪排列）
VerPanel --> Browser : 顯示版本列表\n（深色抽屜風格，非 DataGrid）

opt 回溯操作（Archived 版本）
  User    ->  VerPanel : 點擊「回溯」
  VerPanel -> LayoutSvc: RollbackAsync(versionId)
  LayoutSvc -> LayoutSvc: Archive 現有 Published\ntarget → Published\nPublishedAt = UtcNow
  LayoutSvc --> VerPanel: 完成
  VerPanel -> Page    : OnRolledBack
  Page    ->  LayoutSvc: GetPublishedVersionAsync(MapId)
  LayoutSvc --> Page  : PublishedVersion (rolled back)
  Page    ->  Browser : InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged)
end

User    ->  Toolbar  : 再次點擊「📋 版本」（關閉）
Page    ->  Page     : ShowVersions = false\n_carouselPaused = false\nStartCarousel(_carouselRemainingSeconds)

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 5. 設備詳情抽屜 ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

User    ->  Canvas   : 點擊設備 Widget
Canvas  ->  Canvas   : HandleWidgetClick(widget)
Canvas  ->  EquipSvc : GetLinkConfigsAsync(equipmentId)
EquipSvc --> Canvas  : LinkConfigs
Canvas  ->  Canvas   : DrawerOpen = true
note right            : EquipmentDetailDrawer 展開\n（position:absolute，右側）\n包含 RadzenTabs：\n當前數值 / 工單 / 警報歷史 / 文件 / CustomUrl

Canvas  --> Browser  : render drawer

User    ->  Canvas   : 點擊 Widget 以外區域（關閉）
Canvas  ->  Canvas   : DrawerOpen = false
Canvas  --> Browser  : re-render

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 6. 即時警報（SignalR） ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

note over Hub         : 後台輪詢或事件觸發\n警報條件評估

Hub     ->  Hub      : AlarmService.EvaluateAsync\n(equipmentId, latestData)
Hub     ->  Hub      : 條件符合 → INSERT\nkanban_alarm_records
Hub     ->  Hub      : IHubContext.Clients.All\n.SendAsync("ReceiveAlarm",\nequipmentId, level, msg)

Hub     -->  Browser : WebSocket push
Browser ->   Page    : HubConn.On<>("ReceiveAlarm")\ncallback（catch 防止斷線）
Page    ->   AlarmSvc: GetActiveAlarmsAsync()
AlarmSvc --> Page    : ActiveAlarms (updated)
Page    ->   Browser : InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged)
Browser ->   Browser : AlarmToast →\nRadzenNotification 彈出
note right            : duration: 5000ms\nSeverity: Error/Warning/Info

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
== 7. 設定管理 ==
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

User    ->  Browser  : 導覽至 /kanban/settings
Browser ->  Browser  : MainLayout.IsKanbanActive = true\n(path starts with /kanban/)\nNav link 保持白色
note right            : NavLink 已改為 <a> +\nNavigationManager.LocationChanged\n所有 /kanban/{n} 均維持 active

Browser ->  Page     : KanbanSettingsPage\nOnInitializedAsync()
Page    ->  Page     : PermSvc.HasPermissionAsync\n(KANBAN_SETTINGS)
Page    ->  EquipSvc : GetAllEquipmentAsync()
EquipSvc --> Page    : AllEquipment
Page    ->  MapSvc   : GetAllAsync()
MapSvc  --> Page     : AllMaps（含 Version 欄位）
Page    --> Browser  : render（4 頁籤）

opt 新增/編輯設備
  User  ->  Browser  : 操作設定管理 DataGrid
  Browser -> Page    : OnEquipmentUpdate(eq)
  Page  ->  EquipSvc : CreateEquipmentAsync / UpdateEquipmentAsync
  EquipSvc --> Page  : updated
  Page  ->  Browser  : re-render
end

opt 地圖管理（含版本欄）
  User  ->  Browser  : 查看已匯入地圖列表
  note right          : DataGrid 顯示：\n名稱 / 格式 / 建立時間 / 版本\nFactoryMap.Version ("v1", "v2")
  User  ->  Browser  : 上傳新地圖
  Browser -> Page    : MapImportPanel.DoImport()
  Page  ->  MapSvc   : ImportAsync(stream, fileName, format)
  MapSvc --> Page    : FactoryMap (new)
  Page  ->  Browser  : re-render 地圖列表
end

@enduml
